title: Adobe Premiere 6.0 Portable.rar
description:
A fully functional professional video editing application that can be launched from a USB drive, and takes less than 16MB! No registration or serial number required, just extract the folder anywhere you want, and it&#039;s ready to go!

Adobe Premiere 6.0 is starting to show some age, but it&#039;s still a great video editing application, and is in many ways superior to that bloated and buggy crap that Adobe is pushing these days (not to mention it is much faster!).
